data.description: Update: 02/02/24  Due to home being occupied we can only show during open house.  Please do not disturb occupants.  We might be able to show other times but please schedule a showing appointment.  Thank you  **Seller is open to to credit for interest buydown!!** Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 2,950 sq. ft. home boasting 4-bedrooms and 3 1/2-bathrooms is nestled in the scenic hills of East San Diego Villa Heights, offering breathtaking views and a lifestyle of comfort. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The spacious family room is adorned with large windows that not only fill the space with natural light but also provide panoramic views of the surrounding valley below. On clear days, you can even catch a glimpse of the distant ocean, creating a picturesque backdrop for your daily life. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the large deck that beckons you to unwind and entertain. Perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing with loved ones, the deck offers a private oasis to enjoy the beauty of the outdoors.  This residence is thoughtfully designed, with four bedrooms providing ample space for both family and guests.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 1107 La Mesa Ave your haven in the hills – where panoramic views and an inviting open floor plan create the perfect backdrop for a life well-lived.
